# React is a javascript library to build dynamic and interactive user interfaces
# Developed at facebook in 2011 (facebook ko banany ke liay ya library liki gai hay)
# Currently most widely used js library
# this is use to create single page application(ya single page applicaton create karti hay)
# React update ko save karta hay
# React aik vertual Dom ka concept hota hay
# Jo kaam react sa kia jasakta hay wo normal javascript sa bhi kia jasakta hay
# Ya karny sa pehle apko DOM(Document Object Model) ki knowledge honi chahiye
# React ka Mental Model simple hay
# JS hard to maintain

#     Working of react
# React ma query karna ya DOM ko update karna ya sab react khud karta hay
# React ma choty reusable component banaty hay

#     React VS Javascript
# Js ma apko steps define karni parti hay
# React ma apko sirf final state batani parti hay
# Js ma apko DOM ko manipulate karna parta hay
# React ma apko sirf UI define karna parta hay

# Introduction to components
# kisi bhi bari website ya page ko choty choty hisso ma divide karna component hota hay
# Component reusability provide karta hay

