# react ko create karny ka 2 methods hay 
# Aik CRA(create react app)
# Aik VITE (ya modern tool hay) 
# Is ma cheesy customizible hay 
# project create karne ka bad apni cmd ma kuch cheesy install karni parhti hay (npm install) then server chalane ka liay (npm run dev) use karna hay
# package.json aik meta data file hay project ki jo bhi imported information hay wp package.json ma hote hay
# is ma devdependencies hote hay wo apko download karni but jab ap code karky kisi ko project do gay to us ma is ki need nahi hoti

#     File Extensions
# Humary pass 2 type ki File extension hote hay (JS, JSX)(JS javascript ki file hote hay JSX react ki hote hay)

# React ma jab bhi component banaya jaye ga to function ka bad component ka first word capital hoga ga otherwise run nahi hoga
# functional component ma initially koi state nahi hota hay (state mean ka koi value nahi hoti hay)
# component ka name same hona chahiye file name sa

#     What is JSX
# JSX ka full form javascript XML hay

#     Exporting Component
# jab bhi hum aik component banaty hain to us ko dosry file ma use karny ka liay export karna parta hay
# export karny ka method (export default ComponentName)

#       dynamic component
# jsx humy allow karta hay is ka undr kuch bhi dynamizam kar saky
