#       Fragments
# Fragments mean part(Hissa)
# Fragments ma ap ko main div lagany ki need nahi shrt ya haika react import karna hoga then main div ki jaga React.fragment tag laga dena pir run hoga
# Apko extra Dom add nahi karny pareingay grouping kar ke is ma add kar sakty hay
# is ka short method ya bhi hay ka apko kuch import karne ki need nahi bus main div ko blank chor de


#       Map method
# react ma map method sa data ko UI element ma convert kar sakty hay
# Map ka matlab conversion hota hay
# Aik type ka array ko dosry type ka array ma convert karty hay us ka liay map method ka use kia jata hay
# Is ma apko aik key bhi deni chahiye


#      Conditional Rendring
# ya kafi ziada important hay
# bohat basic hay
# Jesy ka mery pass kuch certain conditions hain jin ka base par mujhe content ko render karna hay
# Ya apko dynamic user interfaces ka faida deta hay
# Is ma ap if else ka use kar sakty hay, ternary operator ka use kar sakty hay, logical operator ka use kar sakty hay

#      passing data via props
# props ka matlab properties hota hay(properties ka short form hay)
# jesy hum html ma attribute ka use karty hain waise hi react ma props ka use karty hain
# jab bhi humy aik component sa dosry component ma data bhejna hota hay to hum props ka use karty hain

#      css module
# css module aik tarika hai jisse ap apni css ko modular bana sakte hain
# is ma apko class names ko unique bananay ki zarurat nahi hoti
# is ma apko .module.css extension ka use karna hota hai
# phir apko apni component ma import karna hota hai
# is ma apko class names ko access karne ka aik naya tarika milta hai
# import karne ka method import styles from './Component.module.css' hota hai

